channel.title: My Friend's Cool Backflip -My First Youtube Video (Rate It)-
channel.description:
Hey,
I just made my first video. It isn't very long but it is a start... I just wanted to show use. It is a video of my friend Marc. We where at the gymnasium. He is doing this cool backflip we learnt. Sorry about the poor graphics it was filmed on my mobile phone. Well tell me what you think.
Also by the way i will be releasing more videos that are longer and have me and my friends doing cool and awsome flips. :P
Link: http://youtube.com/watch?v=PXVy8Qpll4A
~Zandia
